data.description: BACK ON MARKET---PREV BUYER HOME SALE CONTINGENCY FAILED-----This 4/2/2 home is on a double lot with 150 ft on the Water with direct access to Peace River, Charlotte Harbor, Boca Grande (Best Tarpon Fishing in the World) and some of the most beautiful islands in SW Florida.    This Home Features Four Bedrooms and Two Baths with Spacious Living Room, Family Room/Dining Room which gives way to Waterfront Views.    Sit Back and Relax on the Screened Lanai and take in the Sunsets.   This home needs some TLC, in bathrooms and kitchen area.   But the Florida Lifestyle of Waterfront Living could be yours if you make this your home!  This home would make a Great Investment for VRBO/Air BNB, Seasonal or Year-Round Rental.
